{"tid":1813994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然支那人講野猶如放屁但今次黑警們要洗定個屎眼s...","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T16:45:19.000Z","uid":343821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ac7e707b4911667e05d766ed2d4d24c09006e0","tid":1813994,"uid":343821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"新任中國中央政府駐香港聯絡辦公室（簡稱「中聯辦」）主任駱惠寧第一天上班，他對香港傳媒表示中國大陸始終是香港「最強大的後盾」，熱切期盼香港「重回正軌」，但沒有特別提出支持香港警察執法，也沒有指出要「止暴制亂」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51005194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51005194&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=ca5c9fdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51005194&h=4420cd59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51005194</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「重回正軌」</span></span>係包括各方面，要黑警重回正軋...成語都有句：「殺一警伯」...<br />\n呢隻支那辦主任應該好清楚，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔吊死三、五千隻黑警</span></span>佢地係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會悔改</span></span></strong>的！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77df34b404721f10c8fdebe38c61afa0212c870","tid":1813994,"uid":58998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"雖然知你打緊飛機，不過都希望承你貴言"},{"pid":"aa5d7e50d5832e22bd4c11c2d8f7ed1ccc37907d","tid":1813994,"uid":343821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77df34b404721f10c8fdebe38c61afa0212c870","tid":1813994,"uid":58998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"雖然知你打緊飛機，不過都希望承你貴言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:38:2